<item>
            <title>[FELIX-4075] Cleanup InventoryPrinter generated file names in the ZIP file</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FELIX-4075</link>
                <project id="12310100" key="FELIX">Felix</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Generating the ZIP creates files whose names are actually the value of the InventoryPrinter names, aka URL labels, instead of the printer titles previously used. Also the files are not numbered any more.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I pretty much like the numbering and it makes sure the files are unique (should two or more InventoryPrinter services use the same title but different names). &lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
